  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\n- As a user I want to see a message I sent as it appears to others, because that helps me judge how to best format messages \r\n- As a user that increases font size to make it more legible, I want messages to still contain sufficient content to read coherent sentences\r\n\r\nA follow up to #11164 to also show messages sent by user A as collapsed in chat view of user A and make collapsed messages accessible:\r\n\r\n- [ ] Apply collapse message to message coming from chat input\r\n- [ ] Investigate and introduce alternative to fixed physical dimensions to determine collapse\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\n\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n- When sending long message as user A, message appears as collapsed\r\n- When increasing font size in OS, collapsed message still includes full sentence\r\n\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\n\r\n## Future Steps\r\n\r\n\r\n",
